I think the less you can take out of something and the more you can do yourself, it's more equal-interest. So you're not taking out big bank loans, you're betting on yourself and you can sustain everything. Maybe it takes a little longer ‚Äî it's been since 2004 to get to where I am now, with the same team, the same manager. hat's how we did it. There was no rush ever to get giant checks.‚Äù
